comments: I did not use any particular strategy for learning the words. I did not use any help and have no pen or paper near me. I must admit I tried to cheat and write the color behind the alien word for my partner but it did not let me. I did not see any pattern but was wondering the whole time, my partner seemed to get the color more right than me. The learning part was not very hard except to memorize which words end with 'o' and which with 'oe' which seemed kind of random.
